            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Lucretius <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Volt</abbr><ex>inia</ex></expan> Suadullus <lb n="3"/>Alba <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XIIII <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>eminae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>artiae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ictricis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XL <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>XIX <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>estamento</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ieri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ussit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>eres</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zeile 1: kleines I zwischen T und V; Zeile 2: LT- oder LTI-Ligatur (I-longa?), VA-Ligatur; kleines L und V. Auf dem Inschriftfeld ist unterhalb der letzten Zeile noch Platz für eine weitere Zeile frei gelassen. Im Giebel Scylla?, darunter Fries mit Volutenkrater zwischen weiblichen Panthern, am Rand Säulen und Masken. (B): Z. 2: AE 1929: Vol(tinia); Bortlik: Volti(nia).</p>
            </div>
